title: Suspicion (TV, 1957-8) Alfred Hitchcock et al
description:
Surprisingly neglected Hitchcock TV show featuring the best and the brightest. It seems that half of these were broadcast live and never recorded, here you get 18 of 41 episodes. Touch of evil and Voice in the night are particularly atmospheric.

The Bull Skinner
Death Watch
Doomsday
Eye for Eye
The Eye of Truth
The Flight
Four o'Clock (mp4)
Fraction of a Second
The Last Town Car
Lord Arthur Savile's Crime
Meeting in Paris
The Other Side of the Curtain
Protege
Rainy Day
A Touch of Evil
Voice in the Night (avi)
The Way up to Heaven
The Woman turned to Salt

In mpg format unless specified. Low quality, but where else are you going to find this?
